Package element

Class Element

java.lang.Object
element.Element
All Implemented Interfaces:
ElementInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
DynamicElement, StaticElement
public abstract class Element extends Object implements ElementInterface
The Element class is the base class for the objects present in the maze. All elements extend from this class.
